Welcome to Big Ol' Timeline!

It looks like this is your first visit,

would you like to see a quick tutorial?

Big Ol Timeline

This is the chart header. Every column is a region of the world. Hovering your mouse over a chart heading will show you a map of what region that represents. Try it!
If you forget any of the controls for the chart, just click this button.
This is the year bar of the chart. The lower you go, the closer you get to the present. Negative numbers represent years BC.
Every block in the chart represents a power that had control of the region. Hover over the block to see more information about that period of time.
